            <dialog>
                <title>CONTROLS</title>
                <talks>
                    <talk>
                        The game starts in the initialization phase.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        During this phase, you can switch the initial position of any of your characters by selecting them (left click) and clicking on the desired position.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        Don't forget to unselect the character (right click) when you're done.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        When you are ready to play, just click on any empty square to open the main menu.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        Enjoy the experience.
                    </talk>
                </talks>
            </dialog>
            <dialog>
                <title>Jist</title>
                <talks>
                    <talk>
                        Hello adventurers! The situation is critical, some thugs have stolen ogre bones that were buried in the crypt.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        Since then, the village is constantly being raided by the undead...
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        Fortunately, I managed to recover the bones from the thugs.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        You must take them back to their place in the crypt. The necropolis is far to the west of here.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        Good luck, adventurers. All the inhabitants of Nervie are behind you.
                    </talk>
                </talks>
            </dialog>
